{"article_id":"Rl5PiRaUlqbLWxXK","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"On Friday morning ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"after a week of constant drubbing by the press ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Donald Trump did the unthinkable","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"and admitted","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"that he had made a mistake .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"On Wednesday , Trump generated what would have been a major scandal for a lesser candidate","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"when he claimed to have seen \" top secret \" footage of the $ 400 million cash payment","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"the Obama administration was recently reported to have airlifted to the Iranian government on the same day","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"the Islamic Republic released four American prisoners .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Trump immediately cast the money transfer ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"which was publicly disclosed back in January ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"as a hostage payment to a terrorism-sponsoring government .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"\" We paid $ 400 million for the hostages , \"","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"according to CNN .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"\" Such a bad precedent was set by Obama . \"","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"The money was , supposedly , Iran ' s cash in the first place :","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"the $ 400 million was paid to the U.S. by the deposed Shah of Iran","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"in order to buy fighter jets .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"The U.S. froze those assets","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"when the Shah was deposed in 1979 ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"but paid the $ 400 million back to the current government as part of the 2015 nuclear deal .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"But Trump went further","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"then just casting the exchange as something sinister :","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"he insisted","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"that he had seen a video of the plane","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"carrying the cash to Iran .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"\" I ' ll never forget the scene this morning , \"","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Trump said Wednesday ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"describing the alleged footage in detail .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"\" Iran―I don ' t think","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"you ' ve heard this anywhere but here―","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"ran","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"rovided all of that footage , the tape ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"f taking that money off that airplane . \"","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"he Iranians \" have a perfect tape ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"bviously done by a government camera ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"nd the tape is of the people","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"aking the money off the plane , \"","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"rump continued .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"It ' s a military tape .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"t ' s a tape","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"hat was a perfect angle , nice and steady. \"","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"he Iranian government released the tape ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"e claimed ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"so that we will be embarrassed . \"","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"fter some panicked speculation in the media","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"hat the video","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"rump had seen","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"ight have been part of the classified intelligence briefings","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"hat both presidential candidates are now receiving ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"campaign spokeswoman on Thursday told The Washington Post","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"hat Trump had \" merely [ seen ] the b-roll footage","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"ncluded in every broadcast \" of a specific Fox News clip .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Despite her admission ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"rump repeated his previous claim at a Maine rally shortly afterwards . )","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"wo days after Trump first described watching a video","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"hat he apparently imagined in great detail ,","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"he Republican presidential nominee abruptly changed course","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"nd admitted","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"hat the video","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"e ' d seen","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"as widely-circulated news footage of the plane","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"arrying the U.S. hostages in Geneva .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"n campaign as fact-averse","depth":4},{"id":65,"text":"s Trump ' s has been ,","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"he acknowledgement , however unapologetic , of basic reality seems like the dawning of a new era .","depth":3},{"id":67,"text":"hat ,","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"ombined with his newly reinvigorated thank you tour on Twitter ,","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"here he has hardly stopped expressing gratitude in recent days to his supporters ,","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"akes it seem like Trump ' s latest \" pivot , \"","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"hich has never quite stuck ,","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"ay be as simple as acting like a normal human being , capable of recognizing facts","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"nd being nice to fellow humans .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"e ' ll see how long it lasts .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":149,"left":138,"right":148,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":79,"right":137,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":79,"left":77,"right":78,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":77,"left":76,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":76,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":137,"left":95,"right":136,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":95,"left":89,"right":94,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":82,"right":88,"relation":"elabor